'''Setswana''' ke puo ee buiwang mo mafatsheng a [[Aforika Borwa]], [[Batswana]], [[Namibia]] le [[Zimbabwe]]. Ke nngwe ya dipuo tsa semmuso kwa [[Aforika Borwa]] fa kwa [[Botswana]] gone e le puo ee tsewang e le yone ya lefatshe ka bophara. Banni bangwe ba Botswana ba tsalwa ba sa bue Setswana jaaka [[Bakgalagadi]], [[Bakalaka]] le ba bangwe. Ba se ithuta mo mebileng. 

Bontsi ba batho ba ba buang Setswana ba fitlhelwa kwa [[Aforika Borwa]] bogolo segolo mo diporofenseng tsa [[Bokone Bophirima]] (North West) le [[Kapa Bokone]]. [[Batswana]] ba [[Aforika Borwa]] ba ka nna didikadike di le 3.4 fa [[Batswana]] ba Botswana ba ka nna sedikadile le go feta (gongwe 1.3). [[Batswana]] ba [[Namibia]] le Ba Zimbabwe ba palo potlona. Legale ditirelo tsa kgaso tsa [[Namibia]] di gasa gape ka Setswana.

Setswana ke puo ee monatenate, ee nonneng ka e bile e buiwa mo mafatsheng a mane a a mo borwa jwa [[Aferika]]. Baithuti bangwe ba dipuo ba re Setswana ke nngwe ya dipuo tse di matswakabele thata go gaisa tse dingwe tsa borwa jwa [[Aferika]]. 

Setswana se na le manatesha puo a mantsi jaaka [[diane]],[[dithamalakane]] le [[maele]].



